{"tid":1708898,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"軍裝警員配槍設計有三重保險","createTime":"2019-11-11T17:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T17:27:37.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87d1794bf8044999c3eca7f6337d426d50851894","tid":1708898,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"軍裝警員配槍設計有三重保險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jf2gMSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjf2gMSb.jpg&h=96ea99ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmvYVGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmvYVGL.jpg&h=51129728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警察軍裝警員使用的槍袋設計均有劃一標準，使用為左輪手槍，槍袋為直拔式，只能在指定角度才能拔出警槍。一名資深警員表示，槍袋有三重保安設計，有槍形固定模位「夾實」手槍，手槍的撞槌（hammer）以至扳機（trigger）的位置有保護罩遮蓋，以及<span style=\"color: red;\">有扭扣，拉開槍袋前要打開扭扣</span>，以防他人輕易接觸及按動。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，每年警隊亦有防搶槍訓練，<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦有人企圖伸手搶槍，警員需以手按着槍袋，並<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將重心前傾</span></span>，與企圖搶槍者保持距離。雖然槍袋內的鐵片能夾緊槍支，但不排除槍袋可能使用多時，有老化情況，減底保護怍用。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家對槍械有濃厚興趣 但沒有犯法意圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但咪撚學</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e25f31a33ba6f1aec736f88c338ef93df00705ec","tid":1708898,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/364936590541634/posts/948873525481268?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F364936590541634%2Fposts%2F948873525481268%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQX4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=cafa8a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/364936590541634/posts/948873525481268?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bbde7baba87c7f3222e2364be03a10c539dcf697","tid":1708898,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25f31a33ba6f1aec736f88c338ef93df00705ec","tid":1708898,"uid":28970,"l